  ('Son Caliu Beach Bar', 'son-caliu-beach-bar', 'Casual beach bar on Son Caliu beach serving cold drinks, cocktails, and simple snacks. A relaxed spot to enjoy the quieter side of the Palmanova-Magaluf coastline.', '2f8519bc-a24b-4dde-9310-bbb1fc10c8c8', 'a9cccc31-713d-4ad0-a901-11ed36c34683', '', '', '', 'Playa de Son Caliu, 07181', 39.5175, 2.5050, false, 4.1, 'Beach bar. Cold drinks and cocktails. Snacks. Seasonal. Casual atmosphere.', '{}'::jsonb),
