  ('Eroski Son Ferrer', 'eroski-son-ferrer', 'Eroski supermarket in Son Ferrer. Full grocery offering including fresh meat, fish, fruit and vegetables, bakery, and household goods. The main supermarket serving the Son Ferrer and El Toro communities.', '78aa1479-5b41-404b-befa-bf055feca90d', 'e114aefa-938c-44e8-ba8c-5b5123990875', '+34 971 23 43 60', '', '', 'Carrer del Comerç, 07180 Son Ferrer', 39.4985, 2.4695, false, 4.1, 'Full supermarket. Fresh produce. Bakery. Household goods. Open daily 9am-9pm.', '{}'::jsonb),
